But a week won't make a difference.


251
00:19:20.120 --> 00:19:20.954
No, we're doing now!

252
00:19:43.810 --> 00:19:44.769
Keep going, Jack!

253
00:20:55.966 --> 00:21:00.095
Come here, look at me. Look at me.
Remember my promise?


254
00:21:00.345 --> 00:21:01.012
Yes.

255
00:21:22.826 --> 00:21:23.910
